data.description: As you make your way down Kanturk Court, in the highly coveted Newcastle neighborhood, you are greeted by this gorgeous, well taken care of, four bed room home at the end of the cul-de-sac. The large front porch is just right for that morning coffee and has plenty of room for seating or even a swing. When you enter through the front door you will notice that this home features a den, spacious living room and a wonderful dining room that is designed for entertaining. The galley style kitchen has all stainless steel appliances, including a gas stove, newer refrigerator and breakfast nook. The back door leads to the recently updated deck and the yard provides plenty of room for gardening, a fire pit or possibly a pool. Upstairs has three large guest bedrooms and a guest bathroom. The primary bedroom features tall ceilings, massive walk-in closet and a primary bathroom that has a separate bathtub and shower. Come and see it for yourself and make this your new home. No POA/HOA.
